organic.title: MD Imaging
organic.snippet: MD Imaging is a full-service diagnostic medical imaging center with locations in Poughkeepsie and Wappingers Falls, NY. Schedule your appointment today.

organic.title: Welcome to our Patient Portal
organic.snippet: We now provide you with 24/7 electronic access to request appointments, view and manage your medical records, exchange secure messages with our staff.

organic.title: Patient Services at MDI Medical Diagnostic Imaging
organic.snippet: MDI offers, MRI, CT, Ultrasound, X-Ray and interventional procedures. Our wide bore MRI accommodates patients of a higher weight and/or who are claustrophobic.
